graph TD
    Start([Start: Ralph Loop Remediation]) --> Phase1

    %% ========================================
    %% PHASE 1: Diagnosis and Fix
    %% ========================================
    Phase1{Phase 1: Diagnosis and Fix} --> RE_001

    RE_001[RE_001: Fix claude command syntax<br/>Agent: build-python<br/>Target: commands/ralph.py] --> RE_001_Check{Success?}
    RE_001_Check -->|Yes| RE_002
    RE_001_Check -->|No| RE_001_Fix[Fix Issues]
    RE_001_Fix --> RE_001

    RE_002[RE_002: Add session status verification<br/>Agent: build-python<br/>Target: commands/ralph.py] --> RE_002_Check{Success?}
    RE_002_Check -->|Yes| Phase2
    RE_002_Check -->|No| RE_002_Fix[Fix Issues]
    RE_002_Fix --> RE_002

    %% ========================================
    %% PHASE 2: Validation via User Stories
    %% ========================================
    Phase2{Phase 2: Validation} --> RE_003

    RE_003[RE_003: Define User Stories<br/>Agent: test-builder<br/>Target: user_stories/] --> RE_003_Check{Success?}
    RE_003_Check -->|Yes| RE_004
    RE_003_Check -->|No| RE_003_Fix[Fix Issues]
    RE_003_Fix --> RE_003

    RE_004[RE_004: Execute blind testing<br/>Agent: test-user-simulator<br/>Target: Walk through each story] --> TestFixLoop

    %% ========================================
    %% LOOP: Test-Fix Loop
    %% ========================================
    TestFixLoop{Test-Fix Loop<br/>Iteration Counter}
    TestFixLoop -->|All Pass| AuditLoop
    TestFixLoop -->|Failures Found| TestFix[Builder fixes failures]
    TestFix --> RE_004
    TestFixLoop -->|Max 5 Iterations| Escalate1[Escalate to User:<br/>Test failures persist]

    %% ========================================
    %% LOOP: Audit-Test-Fix Loop (MANDATORY)
    %% ========================================
    AuditLoop{Audit-Test-Fix Loop<br/>Iteration Counter}
    AuditLoop -->|First Run| Audit[Test Auditor:<br/>Verify Ralph spawns correctly]
    Audit --> AuditCheck{Audit Pass?}
    AuditCheck -->|Yes & Tests Pass| Complete
    AuditCheck -->|Issues Found| AuditFix[Fix audit issues]
    AuditFix --> RE_004
    AuditLoop -->|Max 3 Iterations| Escalate2[BLOCK Completion:<br/>Audit failures must be resolved]

    %% ========================================
    %% COMPLETION
    %% ========================================
    Complete([Complete: Ralph Loop Fixed])

    %% ========================================
    %% SUCCESS CRITERIA
    %% ========================================
    %% - agentic ralph start spawns a working Claude session in tmux
    %% - Claude session runs unattended without permission prompts
    %% - All remediation user stories pass validation

